## Script Reference

| Script | When to use |
|---|---|
| `scripts/extract_sessions.py --source PATH --chats PATH` | Developer has CLI installed and wants CLI chats included |
| `scripts/extract_sessions.py --source PATH` | Agent-transcripts only (no CLI, or user declined CLI chats) |
| `scripts/extract_sessions.py --chats PATH` | CLI chats only (rare) |
| `scripts/extract_sessions.py` | Manual drop — reads from `ingestion/cursor/projects/` (JSONL) and `ingestion/cursor/chats/` (SQLite) |
| `scripts/extract_txt_sessions.py` | Manual drop — ingestion folder contains `.txt` plain-text transcripts (see below) |
| `scripts/analyse_sessions.py` | Always — runs after extract, produces `analysis_stats.json` |
| `scripts/discover_cursor.py` | Not needed in Cursor — for Claude Cowork only |
| `scripts/import_cursor.py` | Not needed in Cursor — for Claude Cowork only |

